WEBVTT

00:00:45.080 --> 00:00:47.540
Are you going to run away again in the future?

00:00:48.800 --> 00:00:49.760
No, I won't.

00:00:50.080 --> 00:00:53.480
I've decided to stay here and find out who the real culprit is.

00:00:53.600 --> 00:00:54.520
Real culprit?

00:00:55.040 --> 00:00:55.880
That's right.

00:00:56.240 --> 00:00:59.700
The murderer who killed my birth parents is in the Liu mansion.

00:01:01.360 --> 00:01:04.080
I am the daughter of Jiang Huai, the head chef at Fulu Restaurant,

00:01:04.080 --> 00:01:06.920
and Lingwu, the personal maid of Old Lady Liu.

00:01:08.680 --> 00:01:10.000
When I was little,

00:01:10.280 --> 00:01:12.080
they were brutally murdered.

00:01:13.680 --> 00:01:14.760
But it's okay.

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:18.000
Now finally some clues are about to surface.

00:01:18.520 --> 00:01:19.520
Look at this.

00:01:41.440 --> 00:01:43.320
Yiyu, I found it.

00:01:44.120 --> 00:01:45.920
I asked the elders at the market.

00:01:45.960 --> 00:01:46.820
Five years ago,

00:01:46.840 --> 00:01:49.039
Master Liu gathered the most famous craftsmen in the city,

00:01:49.039 --> 00:01:50.840
selected a fine piece of Hetian jade,

00:01:50.840 --> 00:01:53.720
and crafted this unique jade pendant for the young master.

00:01:53.720 --> 00:01:55.400
It was his 18th birthday gift.

00:02:00.320 --> 00:02:01.320
The young master?

00:02:01.920 --> 00:02:02.800
Yes.

00:02:03.240 --> 00:02:07.160
They say the young master's birth mother, Lady Liu, was extraordinarily beautiful in her lifetime

00:02:07.160 --> 00:02:09.280
and shared a deep love with Master Liu.

00:02:09.280 --> 00:02:12.440
That's why Master Liu was especially doting on the young master.

00:02:12.440 --> 00:02:13.770
The whole city knows it.

00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:17.800
I'm afraid it was the master's excessive indulgence

00:02:18.000 --> 00:02:21.040
that made the young master arrogant and overbearing.

00:02:21.280 --> 00:02:22.800
Until he caused trouble.

00:02:28.720 --> 00:02:31.040
Husband, you've been ignoring me for days.

00:02:31.040 --> 00:02:32.600
Have you grown tired of me?

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:37.760
Who was it that desperately insisted on bringing me into this household?

00:02:37.760 --> 00:02:39.040
Don't you hate me?

00:02:39.720 --> 00:02:41.280
Isn't this what you wanted?

00:02:43.840 --> 00:02:44.680
Husband.

00:02:45.040 --> 00:02:48.770
We've been married for days but haven't consummated our marriage.

00:02:48.800 --> 00:02:51.680
Today is such a beautiful day, perhaps we could...

00:02:55.320 --> 00:02:57.680
Husband, I've come to my senses.

00:02:58.200 --> 00:03:00.120
The Liu family is wealthy and powerful.

00:03:00.120 --> 00:03:01.760
You are the eldest son.

00:03:02.840 --> 00:03:05.040
A wise man knows when to adapt to circumstances.

00:03:05.040 --> 00:03:08.400
Liu Sinan is merely a husband in name only.

00:03:08.680 --> 00:03:10.120
Being your wife,

00:03:10.200 --> 00:03:12.600
is my greatest fortune in three lifetimes.

00:03:13.040 --> 00:03:15.240
I was too immature before.

00:03:17.120 --> 00:03:19.600
Please don't hold it against me.

00:03:27.240 --> 00:03:28.300
What are you doing?

00:03:30.600 --> 00:03:31.600
Fire!

00:03:35.200 --> 00:03:36.840
Fire! There's a fire! Help!

00:03:36.880 --> 00:03:37.960
Fire!

00:03:38.120 --> 00:03:40.400
Fire! Fire! Fire!

00:03:40.480 --> 00:03:42.240
Stay back! Don't come any closer!

00:03:42.240 --> 00:03:43.680
Do you remember this?

00:03:44.320 --> 00:03:45.600
It's yours, isn't it?

00:03:47.600 --> 00:03:49.200
Please be seated, everyone.

00:03:50.240 --> 00:03:51.240
Silin,

00:03:51.320 --> 00:03:55.600
this is a birthday gift from your mother and me.

00:03:55.680 --> 00:03:56.680
Thank you, Father.

00:03:56.680 --> 00:03:59.210
You should thank your mother for raising you.

00:03:59.320 --> 00:04:00.380
Thank you, Mother.

00:04:12.120 --> 00:04:16.399
So even the eldest young master of the Liu family gets scared sometimes.

00:04:17.959 --> 00:04:18.880
Tell me.

00:04:19.120 --> 00:04:20.880
Is it yours or not?

00:04:20.959 --> 00:04:22.880
I don't know. I don't know.

00:04:23.120 --> 00:04:23.960
I don't know.

00:04:24.040 --> 00:04:25.880
Something terrible has happened! The young master's room is on fire!

00:04:25.880 --> 00:04:27.680
Help! There's a fire!

00:04:28.480 --> 00:04:30.840
Husband, are you all right?

00:04:31.040 --> 00:04:32.760
Young Master, are you all right?

00:04:32.760 --> 00:04:34.600
Fire! There's fire!

00:04:34.760 --> 00:04:36.320
The Young Master is in shock.

00:04:36.320 --> 00:04:37.960
Quickly, go fetch a doctor.

00:04:38.040 --> 00:04:39.480
Yes, Madam.

00:04:53.960 --> 00:04:54.760
Yiyu.

00:04:55.120 --> 00:04:56.040
Sinan.

00:05:02.560 --> 00:05:04.880
Here's the slow-acting poison you asked me to find.

00:05:04.880 --> 00:05:06.610
What are you going to use it for?

00:05:08.120 --> 00:05:11.050
I've found the murderer who killed my birth parents.

00:05:11.840 --> 00:05:12.720
Who?

00:05:13.160 --> 00:05:14.280
It's Liu Silin.

00:05:16.560 --> 00:05:17.760
How is that possible?

00:05:17.960 --> 00:05:20.240
Although my brother mistreats and abuses his servants,

00:05:20.240 --> 00:05:20.960
but at least he has...

00:05:20.960 --> 00:05:22.560
Stop making excuses for him.

00:05:24.040 --> 00:05:26.160
I know blood is thicker than water,

00:05:26.320 --> 00:05:28.680
but I've confirmed it.

00:05:28.720 --> 00:05:31.120
He's the one who murdered my birth parents.

00:05:31.440 --> 00:05:32.680
Will you help me?

00:05:35.000 --> 00:05:37.159
Since my brother has done such a thing,

00:05:38.000 --> 00:05:39.530
his crime is unforgivable.

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:40.560
However, Yiyu,

00:05:44.600 --> 00:05:46.040
what concerns me most

00:05:46.400 --> 00:05:47.720
is your safety.

00:05:58.440 --> 00:06:00.480
Hey, what's going on?

00:06:00.720 --> 00:06:02.880
There was a fire in the young master's room yesterday.

00:06:02.880 --> 00:06:03.880
The young master was frightened.

00:06:03.880 --> 00:06:05.810
He's had a high fever all day today.

00:06:05.880 --> 00:06:07.120
The master is furious.

00:06:07.120 --> 00:06:09.320
He says if anything happens to the young master,

00:06:09.320 --> 00:06:10.960
we'll all pay with our lives.

00:06:11.880 --> 00:06:13.010
I'll go check on him.

00:06:19.160 --> 00:06:20.600
The young mistress is back.

00:06:20.600 --> 00:06:22.560
You may go now. I'll take care of him.

00:06:22.560 --> 00:06:23.440
Yes.

00:07:01.280 --> 00:07:02.680
Why is your hand so hot?

00:07:03.320 --> 00:07:04.920
Take your medicine quickly.

00:07:22.440 --> 00:07:23.880
Get Liu Silin out here.

00:07:23.880 --> 00:07:25.720
Gentlemen, let's talk this through.

00:07:25.720 --> 00:07:27.400
No need for weapons.

00:07:27.760 --> 00:07:29.600
Hurry up and bring that crazy son out.

00:07:29.600 --> 00:07:32.280
Or I won't be so polite anymore.

00:07:34.880 --> 00:07:35.940
What's that sound?

00:07:36.000 --> 00:07:38.560
Sounds like gunshots.

00:07:49.159 --> 00:07:50.440
What are you doing?

00:08:03.040 --> 00:08:04.880
I'm not dead yet.

00:08:05.280 --> 00:08:07.000
What's going on here?

00:08:08.880 --> 00:08:11.000
Young master, you absolutely cannot go out.

00:08:11.000 --> 00:08:11.760
Why not?

00:08:11.880 --> 00:08:13.720
The police are looking for you everywhere.

00:08:13.720 --> 00:08:15.000
The master is furious right now.

00:08:15.000 --> 00:08:17.600
If you go out now, you'll be in serious trouble.

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:23.880
Mr. Liu.

00:08:24.440 --> 00:08:25.480
Excuse me.

00:08:25.680 --> 00:08:27.410
I apologize for the intrusion.

00:08:27.480 --> 00:08:28.740
Someone reported that

00:08:28.880 --> 00:08:33.320
Liu Silin recently beat a vendor to death on the street.

00:08:33.559 --> 00:08:35.559
I'm here under orders to arrest him.

00:08:35.720 --> 00:08:38.240
Mr. Liu, we understand.

00:08:38.559 --> 00:08:39.720
You're a big name in Yuncheng,

00:08:39.720 --> 00:08:41.159
with vast wealth and influence.

00:08:41.159 --> 00:08:43.690
But when these incidents happen repeatedly,

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:45.800
don't you find it embarrassing?

00:08:46.160 --> 00:08:48.160
The commander is showing you respect.

00:08:48.160 --> 00:08:50.490
You need to show respect to the Commander.

00:08:51.280 --> 00:08:54.440
