Madam.

00:10:43.440 --> 00:10:44.560
What is it now?

00:10:44.640 --> 00:10:46.320
The master is asking for you.

00:10:46.880 --> 00:10:47.760
I...

00:10:56.560 --> 00:10:59.240
Thankfully, Sinan is such a filial child.

00:10:59.440 --> 00:11:02.440
